title: Links in Rebecca's Life
creator: Pansy aka Isabella Alden
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
description: LibriVox recording of Links in Rebecca's Life, by Pansy. Read by BookAngel7. Rebecca Harlowe is a young woman who strives to apply Christ's instructions in the Bible to her daily life and relationships. In this book we witness some of her successes and failures and the effect of her example on those around her.
